reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I like them!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these to take notes and draw models for my health classes and really liked them. However, when I used a mechanical pencil or a sharp pen, some of the sticky note gets scratched out and nothing transfers to the note. It’s not much of a problem though specially if you don’t write hard.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really good for note taking
reviews.reviewText: I used this to study and in my notes and it is a great stationery to have for students! It adheres really well on any surface and doesn't cause any bleeding of ink onto other papers. In terms of functionality, transparent sticky notes perform just as well as their opaque counterparts. They have a strong adhesive backing that ensures they stay in place, even on vertical surfaces. You can write on them with any pen or marker, and the ink will be easily legible. Moreover, they are available in various sizes, allowing you to capture both small and substantial amounts of information.Another advantage of transparent sticky notes is their reusability. Unlike regular paper notes that are often thrown away after use, transparent sticky notes can be easily removed and reapplied elsewhere without losing their adhesive properties. This not only helps reduce waste but also enables you to reuse it multiple times, giving you more value for your investment.Furthermore, transparent sticky notes are durable and resistant to tearing. This means you can trust them to last long without losing their transparent quality or becoming damaged. You can confidently use them in high-traffic areas or situations where they may be exposed to physical stress.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 9, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So clear I lost them :)
reviews.reviewText: So, first off, these stick very well. I use them to write positive affirmation notes to my daughter and reminders on her folders. I put that sticky on her folder on a Sunday evening and Thursday morning, the note was still attached, not crinkled or anything and she has many books in her book bag, so pulling them in and out of her bag should have pulled the note off, but nope, stuck on like a champ.Second, they are easy to write on. I used the Amazon ballpoint pens and they wrote without any issue, no smudging, and it looked beautiful. Have to try other types of pens, and markers to see how they work but so far, ballpoint pens work great on these.Finally, they come in a clear plastic wrap and I'm not saying they are invisible but I lost them somewhere in my house. If they were colored, I could find them and if they were white, I could probably find them so either my vision is completely shot or these pads would win the ultimate game of hide and seek known to man. So when I do eventually find them, wherever they are hiding, I will see how highlighters and markers and other writing utensils work on it.So overall, wonderful product; side note: put it somewhere that it can be easily grabbed and found because once you put it down, have fun looking like a crazy person yelling to clear sticky pads "Where are you?"

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This product is very well priced. However, there is a sticky residue left behind by the adhesive strip. I tried moving it around on the page after a few days and realized the entire page was sticky. I thought maybe it was my book, but I had another brand of sticky notes that did not leave this residue. Overall, good product for transparency, but beware of the residue.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Such a useful tool. Works with pencils perfectly!
reviews.reviewText: I have a terrible habit of writing notes in margins, especially when reading something thought provoking. I have always written notes in books to remind myself to write down my full thoughts, or a poignant quote when Journaling. When borrowing books from friends or the library, these are indispensable and I would recommend them for anyone with my bad habbit, or anyone studying for anything.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought it because of the aesthetic look for my bible study. And it served its purpose. The adhesion is very good. But I may try it on something else to see if it works.
